var JIRASDFMMapper={addMapping:function(){var d=AJS.$("#jiracustField option:selected").text();var e=AJS.$("#sdcustField option:selected").text();var c=AJS.$("#sdcustField option:selected").attr("id");if(this.validateMapping(d,e,c)){var b="/rest/jirasdfm/1.0/fieldMapper/addMapping";var a=JSON.stringify({jiraFieldName:d,jiraSdFieldName:e,jiraSdFieldId:c});AJS.$.ajax({url:b,type:"POST",data:a,dataType:"json",contentType:"application/json",success:function(f){AJS.$("#jirasdfmmappingstable tbody tr").remove();AJS.log(" Mapping deleted is "+d+"->"+e);JIRASDFMTableRowAppender.showTableRows(f);JIRA.Messages.showSuccessMsg("Config Added!")}})}},removeMapping:function(d,e,c){var b="/rest/jirasdfm/1.0/fieldMapper/deleteMapping";var a=JSON.stringify({jiraFieldName:d,jiraSdFieldName:e,jiraSdFieldId:c});AJS.$.ajax({url:b,type:"POST",data:a,dataType:"json",contentType:"application/json",success:function(f){AJS.$("#jirasdfmmappingstable tbody tr").remove();AJS.log(" Mapping deleted is "+d+"->"+e);JIRASDFMTableRowAppender.showTableRows(f);JIRA.Messages.showSuccessMsg("Config Deleted!")}})},getAllMappings:function(){AJS.$("#jirasdfmmappingstable tbody tr").remove();var a="/rest/jirasdfm/1.0/fieldMapper/getAllMappings";AJS.$.ajax({url:a,dataType:"json",type:"POST",success:function(b){AJS.log("Parsing the response and converting them to table rows");JIRASDFMTableRowAppender.showTableRows(b)}})},validateMapping:function(b,c,a){if(JIRASDFMTableRowAppender.isRowAlreadyPresent(b,c,a)){JIRA.Messages.showErrorMsg("The config you want to add is already present, please check your config again");return false}else{return true}return true}};